#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/kafka.adoc
msgid "Let's imagine the following process:"
msgstr "以下のプロセスを想像してみましょう。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/kafka.adoc
msgid "You receive an HTTP request with a payload,"
msgstr "ペイロードを含む HTTP リクエストを受信します。"

